{"tid":1692534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦：自己香港自己救","createTime":"2019-11-04T06:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T06:29:11.000Z","uid":223216,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49bb80ee234ca3a49416b8e359810d5aad0e7fd5","tid":1692534,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"唔係話外國完全無用<br />\n只不過無大台是整個運動的特點<br />\n正正因為無大台，我地先可以堅持咁耐<br />\n無可否認，香港人無軍事，仲要聽緊中共支笛<br />\n係要外國人助攻附助，要外國法案幫手<br />\n但係大家要好清楚一點「外國幫手」「人權法案」<br />\n呢啲只係我地其中一條路，其中一個手段去爭取我地要既野，更加邁向我地要既野<br />\n而唔係外國話我地唔可以做乜就唔做，叫我地做乜就做，俾外國限制，坐以待斃等人救<br />\n香港人係我地既地方，只有真正既香港人先可以話事，唔係港共，唔係北京。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要實踐</span></span></strong><br />\n敵人唔俾我地去商場，要去更多，日日去<br />\n唔俾我地個個星期港島尖沙咀行街，個個星期行<br />\n唔俾貼文宣，貼更多，撕一貼百，一人一張都係返度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要知道如果我地做既野係無用，佢地唔會咁落力去打壓<br />\n<br />\n明白大家都好氣餒，我都係，但係我更期待同大家係煲底相見，識返個前線巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 天琦唔係大台 只係攬炒巴條片見到 提醒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你若放棄 誰衛我城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/04/135224_fd649237bc0299273da6ca202dd03303.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F04%2F135224_fd649237bc0299273da6ca202dd03303.png&h=f2e5b738&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/04/135235_853d9d3620404fd0fbe57b341d43c851.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F04%2F135235_853d9d3620404fd0fbe57b341d43c851.png&h=b25e6e14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/04/135244_7dd5b1f4f86e7b847e52c753a7f36ab5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F04%2F135244_7dd5b1f4f86e7b847e52c753a7f36ab5.jpeg&h=e8cae9f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37c56b83af4c479d88a0fb4b6603a7e2cb67d297","tid":1692534,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"正能量+1"},{"pid":"101c386bbac4ace1a132fd3e63b9f947d3e8fe79","tid":1692534,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:22:53.000Z","msg":"正能量+2"},{"pid":"12c13b4e9531424a7b0a7c4504a671aa3659c707","tid":1692534,"uid":223216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"覺得氣餒就望住手足受傷既相<br />\n香港人真係無得再輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35943872ab11655c03283b9abda0265e4eb3fa47","tid":1692534,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12c13b4e9531424a7b0a7c4504a671aa3659c707","tid":1692534,"uid":223216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"覺得氣餒就望住手足受傷既相<br />\n香港人真係無得再輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"香港人返住工睇緊呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24299d64d5b315f37d455beb665f3d75eabef56","tid":1692534,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4ef336619a96fce20ee0703fc00959e8dae121b","tid":1692534,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35943872ab11655c03283b9abda0265e4eb3fa47","tid":1692534,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12c13b4e9531424a7b0a7c4504a671aa3659c707","tid":1692534,"uid":223216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"